{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "job-portal-api-collection",
    "name": "Job Portal API",
    "description": "مجموعة Postman لاختبار واجهة برمجة تطبيقات Job Portal.\n\n## الاستخدام\n1. استورد هذا الملف في Postman (Import → Upload Files)\n2. تأكد أن متغير `base_url` يشير إلى السيرفر (الافتراضي: http://localhost:8000)\n3. ابدأ بـ **API Home** للتأكد أن السيرفر يعمل\n\n## تدفق التسجيل\n- **باحث عن عمل:** Register → Verify OTP → Login\n- **شركة:** Register → Verify OTP → (انتظار موافقة الأدمن) → Login",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Utility",
      "description": "نقاط عامة للتحقق من عمل الـ API وجلب القوائم",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "API Home",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", ""]
            },
            "description": "التحقق من أن الـ API يعمل.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Job Portal API is working 🚀\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Choices",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/choices/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "choices", ""]
            },
            "description": "جلب قوائم المحافظات وأنواع الشركات للقوائم المنسدلة.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"governorates\": [{\"value\": \"damascus\", \"label\": \"Damascus\"}],\n  \"company_types\": [{\"value\": \"programming\", \"label\": \"Programming\"}]\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Job Seeker Auth",
      "description": "تسجيل وتسجيل دخول باحثي العمل",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Job Seeker",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"full_name\": \"Ahmad Ali\",\n  \"email\": \"ahmad@example.com\",\n  \"phone_number\": \"+963912345678\",\n  \"password\": \"securepass123\",\n  \"password_confirm\": \"securepass123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/job-seeker/register/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "job-seeker", "register", ""]
            },
            "description": "تسجيل باحث عن عمل وإرسال رمز OTP إلى البريد الإلكتروني.\n\n**الحقول المطلوبة:**\n- `full_name` — أحرف ومسافات فقط (عربي/إنجليزي)\n- `email` — بريد فريد\n- `phone_number` — بصيغة `+XXXXXXXXXXX` (9–10 أرقام بعد رمز الدولة)\n- `password` — 8 أحرف على الأقل\n- `password_confirm` — يجب أن يطابق password\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\"message\": \"Verification code sent to your email\"}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Job Seeker OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmad@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/job-seeker/verify-otp/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "job-seeker", "verify-otp", ""]
            },
            "description": "التحقق من رمز OTP وإنشاء حساب باحث العمل.\n\n**الحقول المطلوبة:**\n- `email`\n- `otp` — 6 أرقام\n\n**Response 201:**\n```json\n{\"message\": \"Email verified and account created successfully\"}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Job Seeker",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmad@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"securepass123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/job-seeker/login/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "job-seeker", "login", ""]
            },
            "description": "تسجيل دخول باحث عن عمل.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Login successful\",\n  \"user_type\": \"job_seeker\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"full_name\": \"Ahmad Ali\",\n    \"email\": \"ahmad@example.com\",\n    \"phone_number\": \"+963912345678\"\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Company Auth",
      "description": "تسجيل وتسجيل دخول الشركات",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Company",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"company_name\": \"Tech Solutions Ltd\",\n  \"email\": \"company@example.com\",\n  \"phone_number\": \"+963912345679\",\n  \"governorate\": \"damascus\",\n  \"company_type\": \"programming\",\n  \"website_url\": \"https://techsolutions.com\",\n  \"description\": \"Software development company specializing in web and mobile apps.\",\n  \"password\": \"securepass123\",\n  \"password_confirm\": \"securepass123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/company/register/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "company", "register", ""]
            },
            "description": "تسجيل شركة وإرسال رمز OTP.\n\n**الحقول المطلوبة:**\n- `company_name`\n- `email`\n- `phone_number` — `+XXXXXXXXXXX`\n- `governorate` — مثل: damascus, aleppo, idlib, homs...\n- `company_type` — مثل: programming, civil, healthcare, education...\n- `description`\n- `password` / `password_confirm`\n- `website_url` — اختياري\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\"message\": \"Verification code sent to your email\"}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Company OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"company@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/company/verify-otp/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "company", "verify-otp", ""]
            },
            "description": "التحقق من OTP للشركة. بعد التحقق يُرسل الطلب لموافقة الأدمن.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Email verified. Your company account is pending admin approval\",\n  \"user_type\": \"company\",\n  \"approval_status\": \"pending_admin_approval\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Company",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"company@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"securepass123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/company/login/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "company", "login", ""]
            },
            "description": "تسجيل دخول الشركة (يتطلب موافقة الأدمن أولاً).\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Login successful\",\n  \"user_type\": \"company\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"company_name\": \"Tech Solutions Ltd\",\n    \"email\": \"company@example.com\",\n    \"phone_number\": \"+963912345679\",\n    \"governorate\": \"damascus\",\n    \"company_type\": \"programming\",\n    \"website_url\": \"https://techsolutions.com\",\n    \"description\": \"...\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Response 403:** حساب قيد المراجعة أو مرفوض"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "dj-rest-auth",
      "description": "نقاط إعادة تعيين كلمة المرور عبر dj-rest-auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Request",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/password/reset/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "password", "reset", ""]
            },
            "description": "طلب إعادة تعيين كلمة المرور — يُرسل رابط إلى البريد الإلكتروني."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Confirm",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"uid\": \"MQ\",\n  \"token\": \"your-reset-token\",\n  \"new_password1\": \"newsecurepass123\",\n  \"new_password2\": \"newsecurepass123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/password/reset/confirm/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "password", "reset", "confirm", ""]
            },
            "description": "تأكيد إعادة تعيين كلمة المرور باستخدام uid و token من رابط البريد."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User (dj-rest-auth)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Token your-auth-token",
                "description": "مطلوب عند استخدام Token Authentication"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/user/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "user", ""]
            },
            "description": "جلب بيانات المستخدم الحالي (يتطلب مصادقة)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (dj-rest-auth)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"securepass123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login", ""]
            },
            "description": "تسجيل دخول عبر dj-rest-auth (CustomUser)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout (dj-rest-auth)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Token your-auth-token"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/logout/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "logout", ""]
            },
            "description": "تسجيل خروج عبر dj-rest-auth."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
